headline.main: Gorsuch Willing to Limit Environmental Groups in Land Cases
headline.print_headline: Gorsuch Willing to Limit Environmental Groups in Land Cases

lead_paragraph: An Associated Press review of Neil Gorsuch's (GOR'-suhch's) rulings as a federal judge finds that the Supreme Court nominee has shown a willingness to limit the participation of environmental groups in lawsuits involving public lands.
